NAME OF DAEMON WHICH IS RESPONSIBLE FOR NETWORK MANAGEMENT IN MODERN LINUX SYSTEMS

* networkmanager
- ALLOW THINGS TO BE HANDLED EASILY AND AUTOMATICALLY
- $ sudo apt install nework-manager AND THEN USE $ nmcli
- $ nmcli dev		# LIST NETWORK DEVICES
- $ nmcli dev show	# MORE DETAILED INFORMATION
- $ nmcli con		# SHOW ACTIVE CONNECTION
- $ sudo nmcli con down interface_name		# DOWN PARTICULAR NETWORK INTERFACE
- $ sudo nmcli con up interface_name		# REESTABLISH NETWORK INTERFACE 
